icity well. When it\u2019s surprised or excited, it discharges electricity unintentionally."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It has electric sacs in its cheeks. When they\u2019re fully charged, Pichu plays very energetically."},{"version":"sword","text":"Despite its small size, it can zap even adult humans. However, if it does so, it also surprises itself."},{"version":"shield","text":"The electric sacs in its cheeks are small. If even a little electricity leaks, it becomes shocked."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Pichu stores electricity in the sacs on its cheeks but discharges it inadvertently when agitated or excited. Being yet immature, the Pok\u00e9mon's handling of electricity is rather inept."}],"evo":{"name":"pichu","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"pikachu","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":220,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"raichu","level":2,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"thunder-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/172.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/172.png","capture":190,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":10,"ev":{"speed":1},"forms":[]}